{"word":"μήν","slug":"μήν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μήν</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μέν\">μέν</a></el>] in the phrase <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰ\">εἰ</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μήν\">μήν</a></el> (more accurately <el>εἶ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μήν\">μήν</a></el>) <b>of course, by all means <a href='B:650 6:14'>Hb 6:14</a>.</b><p class=\"br\"/><b><el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μήν\">μήν</a>, μηνός, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a></el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex] <b>month <a href='B:490 1:24'>Lk 1:24</a>; <a href='B:510 7:20'>Ac 7:20</a>; <a href='B:660 5:17'>Js 5:17</a>; <a href='B:730 9:5'>Rv 9:5</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Rv; of a month with a special festival observance <b><a href='B:550 4:10'>Gal 4:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μηλωτή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μηνύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}